move all subdirectories into your arduino/libraries directory and then open the pde sketch file.

or use the embedded Makefile: 
 % make
 % PORT=/dev/ttyACM0 make upload

or if you use an Arduino Duemilanove

 % PORT=/dev/ttyACM0 MODEL=atmega328 make upload

if you use another arduino, please check on :

 % make list

Please check the pathes to your Arduino libraries,your avrdude and avr-gcc toolchain beforehands.

AND USE Arduino IDE <1.0 !!!
